msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 2 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 2 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an2.64-76:0.2"
msgid "7. Sukhavagga "
msgstr "7. Happiness "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
msgctxt "an2.64-76:0.3"
msgid "64 "
msgstr "64 "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc64.1
msgctxt "an2.64-76:64.1.1"
msgid "“Dvemāni, bhikkhave, sukhāni. "
msgstr "“There are, mendicants, these two kinds of happiness. "

msgctxt "an2.64-76:64.1.2"
msgid "Katamāni dve? "
msgstr "What two? "

msgctxt "an2.64-76:64.1.3"
msgid "Gihisukhañca pabbajitasukhañca. "
msgstr "The happiness of laypeople, and the happiness of renunciates. "

msgctxt "an2.64-76:64.1.4"
msgid "Imāni kho, bhikkhave, dve sukhāni. "
msgstr "These are the two kinds of happiness. "

msgctxt "an2.64-76:64.1.5"
msgid "Etadaggaṃ, bhikkhave, imesaṃ dvinnaṃ sukhānaṃ yadidaṃ pabbajitasukhan”ti. "
msgstr "The better of these two kinds of happiness is the happiness of renunciates.” "

#. HTML: </p></article></section><section class="sutta" data-uid="an2.65" id="65"><article><div class="hgroup"><h1>
msgctxt "an2.64-76:64.1.6"
